Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my son\Nis looking at those magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.63,0:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll solve equations with my right hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.77,0:01:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,SUSPECT: TAYOSHI MURAO
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...and write names with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a potato chip
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.82,0:01:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.19,0:01:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And the witness to my alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,is L himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.36,0:02:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ENCOUNTER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.91,0:02:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this? Ryuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure\Nnobody's following you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Now, hurry up already, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The symptoms are getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] I really hope you're not saying\Nwhat you think I'd want to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.72,0:02:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Whoa. Hold it right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I just flew out and checked\Na one-hundred-meter radius around you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and there was no one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.22,0:02:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah, for the last time, I'm sure.\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, but on the news
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,they said they were dispatching\N1,500 investigators to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,They're bluffing.\NYou said so yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were really happening,\Nthey wouldn't announce their arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.53,0:02:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they'd come\Nand investigate secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll buy you some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.24,0:02:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are. Please, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Light, come on! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[chomping loudly]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're really haven't been\Nthat nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[chomping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,[swallows]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You have me looking all over for cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,telling me that I can't even eat apples\Nin the house anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-[chains jangle]\N-[bones crackle]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you eat the core as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chomping]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I might actually write your name\Nin my Death Note and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.95,0:03:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.41,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't laugh, if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Right. That reminds me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got one finishing touch left to add.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. Hey, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,about purse-snatcher and embezzler's\Nheart attacks two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems my family couldn't have had\Nany knowledge of them before they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't that resolve\Nany doubts you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though Kira can control\Nthe time of death,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that there's any way\Nhe could've arranged their deaths
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,without having seen\Nthe broadcast first. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son has come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, so you're gonna keep quiet\Nand pretend to study again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a good grasp\Nof where all the cameras are placed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I only managed to kill\Na purse-snatcher and an embezzler...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,MURAO TA...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...using that trick with potato chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Both of them were guilty\Nof much lesser crimes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,than my previous victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.75,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[male newscaster] Next in...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're watching TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I made sure to kill criminals\Nwhose names and faces were broadcasted
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,when I didn't have access\Nto TV or the Internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is a chance\NI'll look even more suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,of only these lesser criminals\Nend up dying
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,when I'm not receiving information.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.73,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if I kill other petty criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,whose names and faces\Nare broadcast as I watch TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't draw\Nunnecessary attention to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,For this to work
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all I really have to do is remember\Nthe identities of the criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I either see on TV or while I'm online,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,regardless of the severity\Nof their crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.29,0:04:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That way, whenever I go out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,MAINICHI ASAJ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can use that piece of the Death Note\NI keep in my wallet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to kill them at random times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.21,0:05:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect way\Nto deal with these hidden cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.72,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] In the past few days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have listened\Nto all of our audio recordings
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and reviewed the video footage\Nwe captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone over them many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've come to a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Our surveillance\Nof the Kitamura and Yagami households,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,has revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.90,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-[Ryuzaki] Hm...\N-[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.37,0:05:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] We will remove\Nthe cameras and wiretaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All that and we still\Ndon't have any suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to pursue other leads\Nbut we'll get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.71,0:05:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Please,\Ndon't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I only said that we were unable\Nto reveal anything suspicious
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,based on our surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuzaki] Even if Kira was among them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wouldn't make it obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, in fact, it could mean\Nhe was able to continue killing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,without doing anything\Noutwardly suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then you believe that Kira\Nis among one of those families?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've said,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a five percent chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira never stopped killing people,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,even while the surveillance cameras\Nwere in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have no idea how he's been able\Nto commit these murders, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say he could kill someone\Nsimply by wishing death upon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think that any human being\Nwould have shown at least some emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,some sign that they were knowingly\Ncommitting an act of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.01,0:06:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the obvious conclusion is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that Kira couldn't be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,what if he is one of these people\Nwe've been watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he is, we have to assume
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,that his psyche has reached\Ngod-like proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Punishing evil-doers without\Nthe slightest change of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.53,0:06:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost makes me want to believe\Nthat Kira does not exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is just\Nthe wrath of a vengeful god.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But that idea is completely absurd,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,to think that god would need a person's\Nface and name to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,These aren't acts of god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But someone very childish and immature\Nwho wants to pretend they're god.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The mass murderer who calls himself Kira\Nexists somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it and I will catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't count on Kira\Nmaking any mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.27,0:07:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how long we watch him,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,he's not gonna expose himself to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ideally, I'd get to know him well enough
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that he'd admit to me that he was Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and show me how he kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Would that even be possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.58,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds cawing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.96,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light. I've just checked\Nand all the cameras have been removed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them, every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We still don't know if they've\Nremoved all the wiretaps from the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.77,0:08:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this means\NI'm no longer a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.77,0:08:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure L won't give up that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's still working\Nwith the Japanese police,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,chances are my father is working with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or under him, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will have to use my father\Nto find out L's true identity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll eliminate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get rid of L,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kira will be one step closer\Nto becoming the god of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.43,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[birds chirping]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[Sachiko] Light, hurry up.\NYou don't wanna be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't need it, but good luck!\N[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.94,0:08:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't see why you two\Nare making such a big deal out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm relieved. We don't have to\Ndeal with wiretaps in the house anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Well, it's nice to know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that one cause of stress\Nwas resolved before my exam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.79,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,2007 TEST CENTER\NFOR UNIVERSITY ADMISSIONS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I get into university, I will have\Na lot more room to act as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I can focus on finding out\Nwho L really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! The exam will be starting\Nin ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you better hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I planned to get here\Nthree minutes before the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,CIVICS EXAM PAPER
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,-[bell tolls]\N-And... begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[professor] You there, student number 162.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit properly in your chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[Zellogi yawns]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Zellogi] It seems like a lot of Shinigami\Nare observing the human world lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out that Ryuk\Nis being kept by a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking? Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.53,0:11:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a disgrace to the pride of Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.74,0:11:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[Zellogi] No, I'm talking about the human\Nwho's keeping Ryuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would want him as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't pets supposed to be cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[cackling]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're right, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's the story\Non this human, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it a male or a female?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I think I better go\Nand take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.22,0:11:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,2007 TO-OH UNIVERSITY\NENTRANCE CEREMONY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a college student now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.46,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm filled with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.76,0:12:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now for the freshman address,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,freshman representative,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[man] And freshman representative,\NHideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuga] Oh, that's up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Hideki Ryuga, the pop idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.44,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's got the brains\Nto get into a school like To-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look anything\Nlike the real Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd be giving the address\Nwith one other student.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never expected this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.13,0:12:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember him from the exam center.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.67,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He got into trouble\Nfor sitting oddly in his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It seemed like he was off\Nin his own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,As all of us embark\Non this new chapter of our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] The student who've\Nscored highest on the test
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,is supposed to give the speech, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.05,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] I guess both of them\Nmust've had the high score this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] I heard they both had\Nthe perfect scores in all subjects.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] It's hard to believe\Nthere are people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I like the little one\Non the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're so weird, Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how he is dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kyoko] Mhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] Man, these two\Nare total opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] This one looks\Nlike a sheltered genius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,who has been groomed for success\Nhis whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.51,0:13:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,As we embark\Non this new chapter in our lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.64,0:13:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] There's something\Nnot right about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just freaking weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] This guy must be\Nwhat they call a mad genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] Coming to the To-oh\Nentrance ceremony dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Either he's crazy,\Nor he's just toying with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuga]\N...freshman representative, Hideki Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.54,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Light?\NLight Yagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is Chief Soichiro Yagami\Nof the NPA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your respect for your father is matched\Nonly by your strong sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're planning to join the police agency\Nwhen you graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.35,0:14:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you have already got experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing as you've helped the police\Nsolve a number of cases in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you're showing an interest\Nin the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.94,0:14:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm impressed by your abilities\Nand your sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you promise\Nnot to tell anyone about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I have important information\Nconcerning the Kira investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'd like to share with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Where’s this coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it safe to just ignore him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I wonder what this information\Nactually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.84,0:14:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell anyone. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to tell you I'm L.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] What? [gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If he really was L,\Nhe would never admit to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this guy\Nwas a bit strange but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pretty extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[groans] Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[puffs] This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,On the off chance that he really is L,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to act how Soichiro Yagami's son,\NLight Yagami, would act in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd be no reason for him to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are who you say you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,then you have nothing\Nbut my respect and admiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I chose to reveal\Nmy identity to you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,is because I think\Nyou could be of some help to us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Kira investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.85,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The likelihood that you are Kira\Nis just under five percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,something tells me\NI'm not wrong to suspect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're just too perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're Kira, I can't think of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that would put more pressure on you\Nthan this little scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If this guy's really L, like he says,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,then consider me impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.33,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If this guy really is L...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even if he is not L, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-- I can't do anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light breathing nervously]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If what he's saying is true,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it probably means he's already\Nshown his face to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If he were to die\Nright after telling me who he was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,it would only confirm their suspicions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Although it's obvious Hideki Ryuga\Nis nothing more than an absurd alias,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,it still complicates things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I get lucky and it isn't an alias,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,if I try to kill him by simply\Nwriting his name in the Death Note,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I might accidentally picture the face\Nof Ryuga, the pop star,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.41,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and end up killing him instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If this guy doesn't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,he will know for a fact that I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he really L?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he already suspect that I'm Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It' hard to say how much he knows, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What other reason could he have
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,for telling Soichiro Yagami's son\Nthat he is L?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean\Nthat he's still suspicious of the people
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that Raye Penber was investigating\Nbefore he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't see why he would\Nreveal himself to me directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him see any signs of distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,clear my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles] I didn't think the ceremony\Nwould be so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[students chatter]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuga] Hey, Light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's your new friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-Uh... nice meeting you.\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The pleasure was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-What an amazing car.\N-A limousine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure I'll see you on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.49,0:18:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[Light] Yeah. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 1] That kid must come from\Nsome serious money.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[student 2] Plus, he is at the top\Nof the class. Where is the justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[music playing on TV]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, welcome home, Mister To-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.37,0:18:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ryuk] Huh? [chains jangling]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[puffing]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.04,0:18:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! He got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, L.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been so humiliated in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.13,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Hey, why don't you just do\Nthe Shinigami eye deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you should have no problem\Nkilling him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What good would Shinigami eyes do me\Nif this is just a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If I kill him\Nand it turns out he's not really L,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then would be like announcing\Nto the real L that I'm Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think that Shinigami killing people\Nand humans killing people
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,are the same thing because they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want nothing more than to kill him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I do it,\Nit's like asking to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the Death Note can only\Nkill a person whose name is written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not like I can\Narrange for someone else to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.75,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inconvenient!\NThat's the flaw with the Death Note.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Light is usually so calm,\Nbut he snapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be getting to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,At first, I thought\Nonce I found out his name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have him die in an accident\Nor kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, none of that will do me any good,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,unless I know with 100 percent certainty\Nthat this guy is L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's already too late\Nto do anything about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,since he's approached me\Nand introduced himself as L.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how sure I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:20:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the cause of death,\Nif L dies now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.70,0:20:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the police are going to suspect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I underestimated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never even considered the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that he would\Nreveal his identity to me on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He could be telling all the suspects\Nthe same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.04,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, it doesn't even have to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He could have sent a double instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,For L, this strategy\Nacts as a solid defense
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it allows him\Nto confront Kira directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He can defend and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.14,0:20:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.22,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a good move.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I haven't seen the last of Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He will keep trying to move in on me,\Nplaying the absent-minded genius
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and will pretend like nothing is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing manically]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.16,0:20:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason for me to be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, this is proof\Nthat they don't have anything on me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this whole thing is nothing more\Nthan a contest between L and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A match of wits!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,On the surface we will be\Ntwo friendly classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But in reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be investigating each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.43,0:21:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is interesting, Ryuga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.85,0:21:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's my friendship you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gladly accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In time I'll earn your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you've told me\Nwhat I want to know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll be no point keeping you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I will kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,with my hands, if I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[theme music plays]